I get tons of people stopping me in the street in Cape Town again, but instead of asking &ldquo;what&rsquo;s weightlessness like&rdquo; they want to know about Open Source. The answer to both questions? &ldquo;Liberating&rdquo; <img src="/smileys/icon_smile.gif" align="middle" alt=":-)" />
</p>

